The paper discusses the application of cooperative game theory in communication and wireless networks, which falls under the intersection of game theory and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
